snippet.textDisplay:
What Allama Iqbal is to Pakistan, Mehjoor is to us Kashmiris. He made us to take pride in our language and our history. He almost single handedly arose the sentiments of revolution within us. He along with Abdul Ahad Azad told Kashmiris that it is better to die than to live under oppression of any kind.
Walov ha bagwanov novbaharuk shaan paida kar
Phalan gul gath karan bulbul tuthuy samaan paida kar.
Come, gardener ! Create the glory of spring !
Make guls bloom and bulbuls sing - create such haunts !
Although these aren't the best artists to sing his Kalaam still i appreciate the effort.
Mehjoor'as ase Kaesheren henz Salaam.✊
